scripts.convert_dart: quicktype -l dart -s schema ../schema/ausfll_base_schema.json -o ../schema/ausfll_base_schema.dart && quicktype -l dart -s schema ../schema/ausfll_game_schema.json -o ../schema/ausfll_game_schema.dart
scripts.convert_ts: quicktype -l ts -s schema ../schema/ausfll_base_schema.json -o ../schema/ausfll_base_schema.ts && quicktype -l ts -s schema ../schema/ausfll_game_schema.json -o ../schema/ausfll_game_schema.ts
scripts.convert: npm run convert_dart && npm run convert_ts
